458
00:35:59,222 --> 00:36:00,620
Well...

459
00:36:00,701 --> 00:36:02,454
Are you going to sit down?

460
00:36:02,541 --> 00:36:04,499
Yes, I am.

461
00:36:11,102 --> 00:36:15,220
