814
01:04:15,877 --> 01:04:17,231
Dance?

815
01:04:21,557 --> 01:04:22,910
No.

816
01:04:23,837 --> 01:04:25,395
You go ahead.

817
01:04:28,999 --> 01:04:31,149
Go on, Bev, dance with the girl.

818
01:05:57,480 --> 01:06:01,440
What's the matter, Bev?
