835
01:07:41,404 --> 01:07:43,360
You could've had a stroke, Bev.

836
01:07:46,205 --> 01:07:48,435
You're lucky to be in one piece.

837
01:07:48,525 --> 01:07:50,879
One piece.

838
01:07:54,725 --> 01:07:56,476
Bev...

839
01:07:56,565 --> 01:07:59,921
