881
01:11:02,851 --> 01:11:05,524
I haven't had one in four or five months.

882
01:11:05,611 --> 01:11:09,763
And does it... hurt...
when you have intercourse?

883
01:11:11,211 --> 01:11:12,769
Yes, it does.

884
01:11:32,693 --> 01:11:34,250
